{
  "text": "The next proposition says that Hermitian metrics h * k are almost balanced asymptotically. This will be important for us. (Compare ( [CITATION_1] , (3.8)-(3.10))) Proposition 2. For any r > 0, there exists some constant C r,\u03c9\u221e such that",
